comments: Porzingis (DAL) has an arm placed slightly away from his body as he establishes himself in a picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver any contact.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver any contact.
Curry (GSW) maintains a legal defensive position as he defends Doncic (DAL) on-ball.
Green (GSW) cleanly blocks Finney-Smith's (DAL) play at the basket and the body contact is incidental.
Green (GSW) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Kleber's (DAL) path.
Porzingis (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
FInney-Smith (DAL) momentarily places an arm around Toscano-Anderson (GSW) as they both move in the same path during the rebound.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path.
Porzingis (DAL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver any contact.
Doncic (DAL) dribbles in front of Wiggins (GSW) and makes marginal contact with Wiggins at the end of drive.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Porzingis (DAL) as he goes to deflect the pass away.
The ball bounces out of bounds and Porzingis (DAL) is the last player to touch the ball. Possession should have been awarded to GSW.
Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes marginal contact with Bazemore (GSW) as he moves during the inbound play. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Kleber (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Richardson (DAL).

Replay review of the foul called on Bazemore (GSW) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Bazemore makes clean contact with the ball and the arm contact with Richardson (DAL) after the ball is knocked loose is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) jumps A to B and makes contact with Curry (GSW) during his driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) makes slight contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm during his dribble.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Richardson's (DAL) path.
Curry (GSW) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) maintains a legal defensive position on Curry (GSW) during the drive.
